## ğŸ› ï¸ Technology Stack

### Frontend Technologies
- **Framework:** React 18 with TypeScript
- **Build Tool:** Vite (fast development and optimized builds)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS with Shadcn UI component library
- **State Management:** TanStack Query (React Query) for server state
- **Routing:** Wouter (lightweight client-side routing)
- **Form Handling:** React Hook Form with Zod validation
- **Charts & Visualization:** Recharts for cricket analytics
- **Real-time:** Socket.io client for live updates

### Backend Technologies
- **Runtime:** Node.js with Express.js framework
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Database:** In-memory storage (planned migration to PostgreSQL)
- **Authentication:** Passport.js with JWT tokens
- **File Upload:** Multer for media handling
- **Email:** Nodemailer for user communications
- **Real-time:** Socket.io for live match updates
- **API Integration:** Node-fetch for external cricket data

### Third-Party Services
- **Cricket Data:** RapidAPI Cricbuzz integration
- **AI Services:** Custom AI service for predictions and content generation
- **Media Storage:** Local file system (planned cloud migration)

### Development Tools
- **Package Manager:** npm
- **Testing:** Jest for unit testing
- **Code Quality:** TypeScript for type safety
- **Build System:** Vite with hot reload
- **Database ORM:** Drizzle ORM (configured, not yet implemented)

